skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill

des:
Get top picks for local events in Austin, TX from the following feeds:
Do512 (http://do512.com/toppicks)

Feed can be enabled/disabled from the Alexa app via Settings > Flash Briefing.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
